  <brief_title>The Effect of Reinforced Endotracheal Tube on Post-operative Hoarseness Undergoing Thyroidectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Reinforced Endotracheal Tube on Post-operative Hoarseness</official_title>
